<!-- REQUIRED -->
## Decision Filter
<!-- ADAPT: Short checklist used whenever a WO, implementation decision, or trade-off is evaluated. -->
Before approving a shortcut or change, ask:
1. Does this improve or protect the core user outcome?
2. Does this preserve the intended experience quality?
3. Does this stay inside the non-negotiables?
4. If it is a trade-off, is the compromise explicit and worth it?

<!-- REQUIRED -->
## Change Control
